[nomarkup][The bookcase is filled with a myriad of items. Not only books, but a large TV, radio, some decorative vases... Modern books sit upon the shelves, but there are also several occult tomes which line the wall - the faint scent of lignin permeating the air. These books must be pretty old. Several scrolls lean against the farthest shelf on top, and you ponder whether they are made from paper or parchment. A traditional quill is even nestled amongst them, gaining dust with time. What a strange, dissonant fusion of new and old...][/nomarkup]
{$kieran}: Oh my... do you see these books?
<<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited($anastasia) is true>>
